query:
SELECT
            c.id as charge_id,
            c.affiliate_code,
            c.net,
            ac.affiliate as affiliate_user_id,
            ac.revenue_split
        FROM charges c
        INNER JOIN affiliate_codes ac ON c.affiliate_code = ac.id
        WHERE
            c.status = 'succeeded'
            AND c.net > 0
            AND c.due BETWEEN $1 AND $2
